                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310630-112-off600 t18310630-112-cd601"></join>, 1 frock, value 18s.; 1 handkerchief, value 7s., and 1 penny, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18310630-112-victim855" type="victimName">
